title: Captain EO 3-D (Eclipse Comics)
description:
Another 3-D treat from the days of yore!

Captain EO was a 3D sci-fi movie starring Michael Jackson, directed by Francis Ford Coppola and shown as part of an attraction at Disney theme parks, that premiered in 1986. Eclipse released this adaptation scripted and illustrated by Tom Yeates in 1987. This copy of it was provided to me by Kurt N.

Merci Kurt! Merci Tom! Merci scanners! L'obtenir, il des graines!
